BWin.mcc/MUIA_BWin_Save

   NAME
    MUIA_BWin_Save -- [ISG.], ULONG

   FUNCTION
    Define what to load during MUIM_Application_Load and what to
    save during MUIM_Application_Save.

    Must be set to an inclusive or of the following values:

    - MUIV_BWin_Save_DragBarTop
      Save the position of the DragBar (if the DragBar is
      available)

    - MUIV_BWin_Save_AutoShow
      Save the AutoShow value (if one of the DragBar, the Size
      gadget or the Close gadget is available)

    - MUIV_BWin_Save_ShowDragBar
      Save the ShowDragBar (if the DragBar is available) value

    - MUIV_BWin_Save_ShowSize
      Save ShowSize (if the Size gadget is available) value

    - MUIV_BWin_Save_ShowClose
      Save Close (if the Close gadget is available) value

    - MUIV_BWin_Save_All
      Save all the above.

    Default 0 .

    NOTE
     Import and Export are available if and only if
     MUIA_Window_ID is supplied and not 0 .

